review_title: Beautiful art...that I wish was bigger!
review_content: I did an abundance of research before making this purchase. I knew when I first encountered this canvas set...that I wanted it...no matter the cost. I was ready for the size tho, I had scoured every review on here with real time pictures. I am smitten by this piece. I just wish it was offered in a bigger size. If it were larger, it would really make a statement! I rated four stars due to size. Package received timely and no scratches on the canvas.

Very easy to place and set.
